stringi Package installation & building


ICU4c
=====

On Linux:

wget http://download.icu-project.org/files/icu4c/50.1.1/icu4c-50_1_1-src.tgz
tar -zxvf icu4c-50_1_1-src.tgz
cd <icu4c directory>
cd src/
./configure
make
sudo make install


Perhaps this could also be needed:

sudo [edit_cmd] /etc/ld.so.conf

or:

sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libicuuc.so.50 /usr/lib
sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libicui18n.so.50  /usr/lib
sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libicudata.so.50  /usr/lib
sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libicuio.so.50 /usr/lib
sudo ln -s /usr/local/lib/libicule.so.50 /usr/lib


Ferora:
   you may try with `yum install libicu-devel`
   however, it may give you an outdated version of the ICU library

